[normal]2.1 As part of our work for the LGA Transport Innovation Project, we developed a   process of co-design, working closely with the local community, other service providers
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]ex
[normal]ternal
[normal] agencies and other County Council departments. We contributed to the County Council’s Older Person’s Well-being Strategy and worked closely with local members of the UK Young Persons’ Parliament. One outcome has been the widely publicised Transport 
[normal]Self-help Kit which enables local groups or communities 
[normal]to
[normal] 
[normal]undertake
[normal] 
[normal]a detailed audit of existing transport provision and unmet local demand
[normal] and see what solutions they could develop
[normal]. 
