[normal]Hampshire County
[normal] Council experience over thirty years is that good public transport solutions are possible by working in partnership with all elements of the local community. Community engagement is essential to gain support and ensure that provision evolves as needs chan
[normal]ge. A variety of solutions, or to
[normal]olbox approach, is needed to 
[normal]address the needs of different individuals and varying situations. 
[normal]Community engagement is demanding of time
[normal];
[normal] local initiatives require help and advice 
[normal]but produce
[normal] some excellent results. Volunt
[normal]eers
[normal] and the local community have a vital 
[normal]role to play but
[normal] si
[normal]gnificant on-going funding remains a requirement.
